altername_name: TY the Tasmanian Tiger: Night of the Quinkan
name: Ty the Tasmanian Tiger 3: Night of the Quinkan
overview: Ty the Tasmanian Tiger 3: Night of the Quinkan is the third installment of the video game series, Ty the Tasmanian Tiger. It is the only game in the series to be published by Activision instead of Electronic Arts, which published the game's two predecessors. It was developed by Krome Studios and was released for PlayStation 2, GameCube, Xbox and Game Boy Advance.
